jacdac.AcidityReg.Acidity:
Read-only pH u4.12 (uint16_t). The acidity, pH, of water.
* ```
const [acidity] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u4.12")
```
jacdac.AcidityReg.AcidityError:
Read-only pH u4.12 (uint16_t). Error on the acidity reading.
* ```

```
jacdac.AcidityReg.MaxHumidity:
Constant pH u4.12 (uint16_t). Highest acidity that can be reported.
* ```
const [maxHumidity] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u4.12")
```
jacdac.AcidityReg.MinAcidity:
Constant pH u4.12 (uint16_t). Lowest acidity that can be reported.
* ```

```
modules.AcidityClient: A sensor measuring water acidity, commonly called pH.
modules.AcidityClient.maxHumidity: Highest acidity that can be reported.
modules.AcidityClient.minAcidity: Lowest acidity that can be reported.
modules.AcidityClient.onAcidityChangedBy: Run code when the acidity changes by the given threshold value.
